  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil.",
    "Add the snow peas and cook for 3-5 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Drain the peas and rinse with cold water.",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together the yogurt, lemon juice, garlic, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and red onion.",
    "Add the feta cheese and stir until combined.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the top and toss to coat.",
    "Serve the snow peas in a bowl and top with the yogurt sauce.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley and serve immediately."
